import PyPDF2

pdf_path = '/workspace/benchmark/datasets/3-DoLa/DoLa-main/paper.pdf'
reader = PyPDF2.PdfReader(pdf_path)
num_pages = len(reader.pages)

# Extract the first 3 pages for overview
text = ''
for i in range(min(3, num_pages)):
    text += reader.pages[i].extract_text() + '\n---PAGE---\n'

print(text[:2000])
